D.melanogaster TADs.

Source: R/utilities.R
TADs_Domains.gnr.Rd

Drosophila Melanogaster TADs on chromosome 2R and 2L (F.Ramirez, 2018)

Usage

data(TADs_Domains.gnr)

Format

An object of class GRanges.

Examples

data(TADs_Domains.gnr)
TADs_Domains.gnr
